(6, 'all', 'IDN ELOTTERY', 'idn-elottery', 'events/01JVHQ4SZWAKXG36ZED3GFEHWR.png', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif\" >IDN E-LOTTERY SPIN SURPRISE CASH DROP</span ></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif\" >Spin Surprise Cash Drop oleh IDN E-Lottery akan berlangsung mulai 1 Mei 2025 hingga 31 Mei 2025 setiap hari, pukul 00:00 WIB hingga 23:59 WIB. Total hadiah cash drop adalah sebesar Rp 1,000,000,000 dan akan dibagikan kepada pemain yang beruntung setiap harinya.</span ></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif\" >Permainan yang Berlaku untuk Promosi Ini:</span ></p><div align=\"left\"><table style=\"border: none; border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >DAVINCI ROLLER</span ></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >BLOOD MOON</span ></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >DRAGON 5D</span ></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >EAGLE LOTTERY</span ></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >(Jackpot)</span ></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" > MEGA PRIZE 4D<br />(Jackpot 4D) </span></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" > MAGICAL PUPPET<br />(Jackpot) </span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >UNIVERSE 6D</span ></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >(Jackpot 6D)</span ></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >KING PALACE</span ></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >(Jackpot)</span ></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" > HAWAII BINGO<br />(Jackpot) </span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" > SUPER MAGIC 5D<br />(Jackpot 5D) </span></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" > TEMPLE PALACE<br />(Jackpot) </span></p></td><td style=\"border: solid #000000 0.75pt\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\" font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; \" >NAVAL BOMBER</span ></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif\" >Memainkan permainan JACKPOT memberi Anda kesempatan untuk memenangkan &nbsp;</span ><span style=\"font-size: 11px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\" >CASH DROP dan JACKPOT</span ></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif\"><strong>Syarat dan Ketentuan</strong> : </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif\" >1. Mainkan permainan yang terkualifikasi selama periode promosi akan mempunyai kesempatan mendapatkan hadiah secara acak.</span ></p><p><span