 Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black; font-size: 11px; \" >46-75</span ></p></td><td style=\" width: 24.9778%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align: bottom; \" ><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: normal; \" ><span style=\" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black; font-size: 11px; \" >50.000</span ></p></td><td style=\" width: 20.0222%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align: bottom; \" ><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: normal; \" ><span style=\" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black; font-size: 11px; \" >30</span ></p></td><td style=\" width: 35.7979%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align: bottom; \" ><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: normal; \" ><span style=\" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black; font-size: 11px; \" >1.500.000</span ></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\" width: 45.8601%; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; \" ><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: normal; \" ><span style=\" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; \" >TOTAL</span ></p></td><td style=\" width: 20.0223%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; \" ><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: normal; \" ><span style=\" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; \" >75</span ></p></td><td style=\" width: 35.7979%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; \" ><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: normal; \" ><span style=\" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; \" >25,000,000</span ></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >&nbsp;</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\"><strong><u>Syarat dan Ketentuan:</u></strong></span></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >1. SLOT MANIA Turnamen oleh Pragmatic Play dengan hadiah senilai Rp 8.25 Miliar yang akan dibagikan kepada 24.750 Pemain Teratas dengan skor tertinggi di papan peringkat selama periode promosi.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >2. SLOT MANIA Turnamen dimulai dari 19/02/2025 hingga 14/01/2026, setiap hari antara 06:00 - 23:59 WIB.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >3. Semua permainan Pragmatic Play memenuhi syarat untuk promosi ini, kecuali Slot Mania High Flyer, Spaceman, Big Bass Crash, Diamonds are Forever 3 Lines, Irish Charms, Money Roll, Permainan Meja.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >4. Pemenang turnamen ditentukan berdasarkan total nilai taruhan tertinggi selama periode promosi.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >5. Skor = Total jumlah taruhan selama periode promosi.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >6. Tidak ada taruhan minimum yang diperlukan untuk promosi ini.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >7. Jika ada dua atau lebih pemain dengan skor identik di papan peringkat turnamen, pemain yang pertama kali mencapainya akan mendapatkan posisi lebih tinggi di papan peringkat.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >8. Papan peringkat turnamen dibuat dalam permainan yang memenuhi syarat dan diperbarui secara real-time.</span ></p><p style=\" margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 8pt; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Calibri\', sans-serif; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px\" >9. Pragmatic Play berhak untuk mengubah, menangguhkan, atau membatalkan promosi ini kapan saja tanpa pemberitahuan sebelumnya.</span ></p>', '2025-05-18 12:56:28', '2025-05-18 12:56:28');
INSERT INTO `events` (`id`, `label`, `title`, `slug`, `banner`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
